chart_description: This chart displays the rate of dictionary operations per second, including creations, deletes, destructions, garbage collections, inserts, searches, traversals, and walkthroughs.

dimension_descriptions.creations: The rate at which dictionary entries are created.
dimension_descriptions.deletes: The rate at which dictionary entries are deleted.
dimension_descriptions.destructions: The rate at which the dictionary itself is destroyed.
dimension_descriptions.garbage_collections: The rate at which the dictionary is cleaned up by removing unused entries.
dimension_descriptions.inserts: The rate at which new entries are added to the dictionary.
dimension_descriptions.searches: The rate at which entries are searched for in the dictionary.
dimension_descriptions.traversals: The rate at which all entries in the dictionary are traversed.
dimension_descriptions.walkthroughs: The rate at which all entries in the dictionary are walked through in depth-first order.
